title: BRIEF-Cytokinetics Qtrly Net Loss Per Share $0.75
text:
Feb 15 (Reuters) - Cytokinetics Inc:
* CYTOKINETICS, INC. REPORTS FOURTH QUARTER 2017 FINANCIAL RESULTS
* ‍ENROLLMENT IN GALACTIC-HF ON TRACK UNDER COLLABORATION WITH AMGEN; FINALIZING PLANS FOR SECOND PHASE 3 CLINICAL TRIAL IN 2018​
* ‍COMPANY ANTICIPATES CASH REVENUE WILL BE IN RANGE OF $17 TO $23 MILLION FOR 2018​
* QTRLY NET LOSS PER SHARE $0.75 * Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $-0.70 -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* FY2018 REVENUE VIEW $25.6 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
